  <section>
    <h2>6. Template Customizations & Accessibility</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Improved color contrast and added `aria-labels` for navigation.</li>
      <li>Enhanced semantic HTML structure (e.g., using `<section>`, `<article>`).</li>
      <li>All images use meaningful `alt` attributes.</li>
      <li>Keyboard navigation enabled using `tabindex` and skip links.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>7. Four Extras Demonstrated</h2>
    <ol>
      <li><strong>Dark Mode Toggle</strong>: Toggle theme using a button and CSS variables.</li>
      <li><strong>Animated Skill Bars</strong>: Skills animate when visible on scroll.</li>
      <li><strong>Project Modal Viewer</strong>: Click to open project details in modal.</li>
      <li><strong>Form Validation</strong>: JS-powered form field validation with feedback.</li>
    </ol>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>8. Example Extra: Dark Mode Toggle</h2>
    <button id="darkToggle">Toggle Dark Mode</button>
    <script>
      const toggle = document.getElementById('darkToggle');
      toggle.addEventListener('click', () => {
        document.body.classList.toggle('dark-mode');
      });
    </script>
  </section>

